{"type": "article", "id": 16970, "title": "气垫长椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-03T06:00:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000342B86gGoxMEbqID3C5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张看起来像是一个充气垫的椅子实际是用金属材质制成，来自英国金斯顿大学的 Connor Holland，不过，单就这一点就足够吸引人。他用液压成型技术将座位压成了一毫米的厚度，有点像漂浮在空气中。座椅上两条看起来很自然的折痕，是用高压清洗机向金属板注水，将两层金属板分开，形成三块凸起的结构，更适合人坐下去。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144212iqtpJewa5bSuAWgP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"638\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144213JRLmqf1vhMDXyjG6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"596\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72860636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144213SvbNQdVFtEec9RqA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261442142NHUXLMTED9qvuhz.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"638\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144214RwxneBVO4yk8Kb6D.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}